  "keyFeatures": [
    "Compile-time annotation processing with JavaPoet — zero runtime reflection per command invocation",
    "Multi-platform support: Standalone Java, Bukkit/Spigot, and Paper (Brigadier)",
    "Hierarchical subcommands via @Subcommand on methods and nested static classes",
    "Built-in tab-completion suggestion routing via @Suggest",
    "Pluggable argument resolvers with type hierarchy, interface, and dynamic provider matching",
    "Validation module with @Min, @Max, and @ValidateWith for parameter-level validation",
    "Customizable error and message formatting via overridable formatMessage()",
    "SPI extension points for ParameterAnnotationHandler, MethodAnnotationHandler, and TypeSupport",
    "CommandInfo introspection for generating help menus at runtime",
    "BOM (Bill of Materials) for simplified multi-module version management"
  ],
